" mimic the behavior of /%Vfoobar which searches within the previously
" selected visual selection
" while in search mode, pressing / will do this
vnoremap / <Esc>/\%><C-R>=line("'<")-1<CR>l\%<<C-R>=line("'>")+1<CR>l
vnoremap ? <Esc>?\%><C-R>=line("'<")-1<CR>l\%<<C-R>=line("'>")+1<CR>l

